short_description: The challenge for this round is to make a track using Six Sines by baconpaul.
long_description: Six Sines is a small synthesizer which explores audio rate inter-modulation of signals, https://github.com/baconpaul/six-sines. Your challenge for this round is to **make a track using Six Sines**.
